				<td colspan="2"><span>This wouldn't work for me because I'm so accustomed to using the F keys to target group members (F1-F6), targetting nearest PC and NPC's (F7-F8) and switching camera angles (F9). I don't want to take away that functionality for merely allowing more hotkeys but that's just me.
<br />

<br />
I have a number of hotkey banks setup for each scenario I'm in. If grouped I only have my most important hotkeys setup for /stopsong, cast #, that way I can have more macros for /gsay's, /assists and such. If I'm soloing I can use the whole bank of hotkeys and have two left over for tracking or whatever.</span></td>
