				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Alternative to Hot Keys<a name="45050"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 8 04 9:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The main reason I see that people would want to change (not rearrange) their hotkeys is because they'd like to use their hotkeys for something other than songs. For example having up to 10 messages/abilities on your hotkeys IMMEDIATELY instead of having to switch to another pad and back to your song hotkey pad. It's sort of like adding another 8 hotkeys to your song hotkey pad.
<br />

<br />
Wouldn't 10 slots for songs be nicer than the current 8 on your song bar?
<br />
Wouldn't 10 slots for your messages/abilities be nicer than the current 2 on your song hotkey pad?
<br />

<br />
That being said, I don't intend to change my key settings as my bard isn't the only character I play and changing key setting affects all your characters currently.</span></td>
